Package tech.hiddenproject.progressive.exception

Contains progressive exceptions.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    AnnotationException
    Thrown if exception connected with some annotation.
    BeanCircularDependencyException
    Thrown if bean has some circular dependency.
    BeanConflictException
    Thrown if more than one bean of given type has been found, but no bean name specified.
    BeanDuplicationException
    Thrown if bean with specified name and type already exist in DIContainer.
    BeanNotFoundException
    Thrown if bean is not presented in DI container.
    BeanUndefinedException
    Thrown if exception is undefined.
    CriteriaException  
    GameException
    Thrown from Game.
    GameScriptException
    Thrown from GameScript.
    StateMachineException
